org.ode4j.ode
Interface DAABBC

All Known Implementing Classes:
DAABB
public interface DAABBC

Immutable interface for AABBs (Axis-aligned bounding boxes), as defined in DAABB.

Axes are numbered from 0 to 2.

Author:
Tilmann Zaeschke
